    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s best suited for someone looking for a cheap runabout, first project, or handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s not perfect and it shows its age, but it still has plenty to offer the right buyer who wants something affordable and straightforward. If you\u2019re after a budget-friendly car with potential and no nonsense, this could be a great fit.",
