    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Straightforward, mechanically honest driver with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels solid for its age. Not a show car, but it\u2019s the kind of well-used machine that still does its job and responds well to regular maintenance. A great budget commuter, winter beater, or project platform for someone who appreciates a car with character and a proven drivetrain. Priced fairly for a quick sale.",
