    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with old-school charm, this car has the kind of presence that turns an ordinary driveway into the start of a story. It\u2019s an affordable way into ownership for someone who sees potential, whether you\u2019re after a budget commuter, a hands-on project, or a dependable set of wheels with plenty of character. The body lines still carry plenty of appeal, the cabin offers a familiar, honest feel, and there\u2019s real satisfaction here for the next owner ready to give it the attention it deserves. If you appreciate value, grit, and the opportunity to make something your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
